The paper presents a fully automatic segmentation pipeline for myocardial segmentation in full-cycle 2-D MCE data using random forests guided by a shape model. This involves image processing, statistical shape modeling, and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is computer vision (cs.CV), followed by machine learning (cs.LG), medical imaging (cs.ME), multimedia (cs.MM), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
